channel.title: Rocca - A Way Out [Remix Comp] (1st, 2nd & 3rd prize =$$$)
channel.description:
Hey guys! I was hoping this track: https://soundcloud.com/roccasounds/a-way-out ![image|500x500](upload://dMRZylA6KoOrM1a4yRbvAwDNjQ5.jpeg) would make it for April staff picks and hold a remix comp but unfortunately it didn’t, however I still choose to hold this comp!
Track info: Chill/tropical house sorta style track, with vocal chops and an orchestral breakdown. Very catchy and mixed and mastered to perfection.
Here are the rules:
Change the track any way you want whilst keeping the tracks originality and recognisability.
You must title it “Rocca - A Way Out [(Your name remix)
You must repost the track and be following me (this is optional but it is required to be eligible for 1st 2nd & 3rd prizes)
Competition timeline: You have until June 3rd (exactly a month from now) [This May be extended]
1st 2nd & 3rd will all win a prize:
1st = $30 aud 2nd = $20 aud 3rd $10 aud
Prize will be sorted through PayPal.
Remix here: https://app.auxy.co/projects/oGGpK5wgZAhKaDiCUWhtWw==
